<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>jiào huì yào fā guāng 迦南1260</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 jiào huì shì jīn dēng tái jiào huì shì zhēn guāng chéng zào zài shān shàng shì bù néng bèi yǐn cáng
 wǒ men yào gāo jǔ zhēn lǐ bǎ shí jià chuán yáng chóu dí kàn jiàn bì jīng huāng
 jiào huì shì jīn dēng tái jiào huì shì zhēn guāng yào bǎ zhè máng máng de hēi yè quán zhào liàng
 gěi mí lù de rén dài lái yǒng yuǎn de fāng xiàng jiào huì yào fā zhēn guāng</lyrics>
